theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "Log #1
Perfection.
This project is the apotheosis of our people. It is our ark. I’ve heard enough of conjurers and deniers, telling the world that each has their place. No, each must find their place! God is not our origin, but our goal! That is what He intended for us, and that is what I intend to fulfill.
"

