theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "Log #9
Failure. Utter, predictable failure.
God, I’ve done what You’ve asked of me. The lines herein were generated not by silica, but by flesh - my own two hands. To make this calculus was my cross to bear… such wasted time. Imperfect hands, God. 
I am not worthy.
"

