theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("3_7af8p")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
text = "Log #10
Isamu was right. The narrative is theirs. Is that what God must feel? Such complete, overwhelming disappointment?
I chose to achieve, and I failed. I do not regret my flight, but I shall not burn my wings.
I choose to turn back.
*/
"

